  "texts": [
    "Despite the benefits, our work has some limitations, including data scarcity which affects the generality of our model.",
    "Looking ahead, future research will aim to enhance our model by incorporating more modalities such as pain level, palpation findings, general observations, wound area and volume, and patient demographics.",
    "Addressing data overlaps in wound location will also be a priority to enhance classification accuracy.",
    "Our efficient wound care algorithm has significant potential for automation in wound healing systems, offering cost-effectiveness and aiding clinicians in prompt diagnosis and development of suitable treatment plans.",
    "Especially in resourcescarce areas, AI-enabled wound analysis can contribute to rapid diagnosis and quality treatment."
